*gource-0.43 (26 Nov 2014)

  26 Nov 2014; Yixun Lan <dlan@gentoo.org> +gource-0.43.ebuild:
  version bump, bug 517724, update libsdl2 as new dep

  18 Sep 2013; Diego E. Pettenò <flameeyes@gentoo.org> gource-0.40.ebuild:
  Fix bug #479896. Patch by Enrico Tagliavini.

*gource-0.40 (16 Jul 2013)

  16 Jul 2013; Justin Lecher <jlec@gentoo.org> +gource-0.40.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  Version Bump

